From 42570b02b50609157153372f11ad4967577e9358 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: JaehyeonLee <ljhhasang@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 07:31:33 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add KVM support for CoFunc split containers

---
